headline: 3 Monster Stocks to Hold for the Next 10 Years
summary: None of these three stocks are conventionally cheap, but they all have huge growth potential from megatrends already in place, making them attractive stocks for investors to buy for the long term.  Here's why electronic design automation (EDA) company Synopsys (NASDAQ: SNPS), design and product management software company PTC (NASDAQ: PTC), and advanced composite materials company Hexcel (NYSE: HXL) are stocks worth taking long-term positions on.
